<ab facs="#facs_319_r1l34">ew das <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> alſpalde auch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Alſo <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
